title: GDM1 exo: GDM_exosome_1st_Trimester_11.3_weeks
extract_protocol_ch1: RNA was extracted using the miRNeasy Mini Kit and TRIzol LS Reagent for exosomes following the manufacturer's instructions.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Libraries were constructed using the TruSeq® SmallRNA Library Prep Kit, following the manufacturer’s instructions. A total of 100 to 300 ng of exosomal RNA was used as input for library construction.
data_processing: Remove index and adaptor sequences using TagCleaner (version 0.16)
data_processing.1: Trim reads to 28 nucleotides using FASTX-Toolkit (version 0.0.14)
data_processing.2: miRNAs were identified using the miRDeep2 program (version 2.0.0.7), using the deafult parameters with the exception of allowing for 1 mismatch and discarding read less than 16 nucleotides in length.
data_processing.3: Raw miRNA counts were normalised and statistically anlaysed using the DESeq2 package (version 1.18.1) in R (version 3.2.2)
data_processing.5: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: Comma-delimited file containing raw miRNA counts
